<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Journal Index | Dioko & Sons</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://googleapis.com" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        html { font-size: 90%; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', Didot, Georgia, serif;
            color: #222222;
            background-color: #fcfcfc;
            line-height: 1.75;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        .container { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 0; }
        nav { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px; font-size: 1.1rem; }
        nav a { color: #555555; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 12px;; }
        nav a:hover { color: #111111; text-decoration: underline; }
        
        header { margin-bottom: 60px; text-align: center; }
        h1 { font-size: 3.2rem; font-weight: 500; color: #111111; }
        .tagline { font-size: 1.2rem; font-style: italic; color: #666666; margin-top: 0px; }

        .post-entry { margin-bottom: 50px; padding-bottom: 40px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea; }
        .post-entry:last-of-type { border-bottom: none; }
        
        .meta-date { font-family: -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 0.85rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: #888888; font-weight: 600; display: block; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .post-entry h2 { font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        .post-entry h2 a { color: #111111; text-decoration: none; }
        .post-entry h2 a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
        .post-summary { font-size: 1.1rem; color: #444444; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        
        .read-more { font-size: 1rem; font-style: italic; color: #111111; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }
        .read-more:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

        footer { text-align: center; color: #999999; margin-top: 100px; }
        footer p { font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 5px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <nav>
            <a href="index.html">About us</a>
            <a href="news.html">Updates and ideas</a>
            <a href="contact.html">Contact Us</a>
        </nav>
        <header>
            <h1>Updates and ideas</h1>
            <p class="tagline">An occasional re-examination of contemporary insights, perspectives, and paradigms.</p>
        </header>
        <main>
            <article class="post-entry">
