            </article>
            <article class="post-entry">
                <span class="meta-date">May 12, 2026</span>
                <h2><a href="posts/foundational-quality.html">The Pillars of Structural Integrity</a></h2>
                <p class="post-summary">Examining why deliberate, low-maintenance technology workflows consistently outperform transient, high-overhead industry trends over long horizons...</p>
                <a class="read-more" href="posts/foundational-quality.html">Read Article &rarr;</a>
            </article>
        </main>
        <footer>
            <p>Unit 2904-05, 29/F, Universal Trade Centre, 3 Arbuthnot Road, Central, Hong Kong S.A.R</p>
            <p>&copy; 2026 Dioko & Sons. All rights reserved.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
